---
import { SITE_DISCLAIMER } from "../../consts";
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>美股科技板块观察：AI 算力主线仍需结合估值和盈利验证 - 398的美股策略</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { margin: 0; font-family: Arial, "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif; color: #111827; background: #ffffff; }
      header { border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
      nav { width: min(1040px, calc(100% - 48px)); min-height: 72px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 24px; }
      nav a { color: #111827; text-decoration: none; }
      .brand { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; }
      .links { display: flex; gap: 28px; font-size: 15px; }
      article { width: min(760px, calc(100% - 48px)); margin: 0 auto; padding: 72px 0 112px; }
      .back { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 38px; color: #1d4ed8; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
      h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 38px; line-height: 1.35; letter-spacing: 0; }
      .meta { margin: 18px 0 48px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
      h2 { margin: 44px 0 14px; font-size: 23px; }
      p, li { color: #4b5563; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.95; }
      ul { padding-left: 22px; }
      .disclaimer { margin-top: 52px; padding-top: 28px; border-top: 1px solid #dfe3e8; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; }
      footer { padding: 30px 24px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; }
      footer a { color: inherit; }
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        nav { width: calc(100% - 36px); min-height: 64px; }
        article { width: calc(100% - 36px); padding: 52px 0 80px; }
        h1 { font-size: 31px; }
        .meta { margin-bottom: 36px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <a class="brand" href="/">398的美股策略</a>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="/">首页</a>
          <a href="/disclaimer/">免责声明</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <article>
      <a class="back" href="/reports/">← 返回研报与观点</a>
      <h1>美股科技板块观察：AI 算力主线仍需结合估值和盈利验证</h1>
      <p class="meta">2026-05-24 · 市场观点</p>

      <h2>观点摘要</h2>
      <p>
        AI、半导体、云计算和数据中心仍是美股科技板块的重要方向，但短期价格与盈利预期之间的差距需要持续观察。
      </p>

      <h2>市场观察</h2>
      <p>
        科技板块近期仍受到企业资本开支、财报表现、利率变化和市场风险偏好的共同影响。后续重点关注业绩兑现情况，以及板块内部表现是否继续分化。
      </p>

      <h2>风险提示</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>企业支出或终端需求低于市场预期。</li>
        <li>估值处于较高位置，波动可能放大。</li>
        <li>利率和市场情绪变化可能影响科技板块表现。</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="disclaimer">{SITE_DISCLAIMER}</div>
    </article>

    <footer>
      © 2026 398的美股策略 · <a href="/disclaimer/">免责声明</a>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
